            <div class="section-component">
				<div class="step-icon"><span>1</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs hidden-sm">1.</span> 在 Azure 官网 www.azure.cn，点击页面右上角的“我要购买”，就可以开始申请了。</h2>
					<a href="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/azure-1rmb-trial-application-and-signup-and-new-step_01.jpg" id="azure-1rmb-trial-application-and-signup-and-new-step_01" target="_blank"><img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/azure-1rmb-trial-application-and-signup-and-new-step_01.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
					<p>请点击<a href="/pricing/pia/" id="pricing-billing-pia-signup_pia" target="_blank">我要购买</a></p>
				</div>
            	<div class="clearfix"></div>
				<div class="step-icon"><span>2</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs hidden-sm">2.</span> 随后我们来到<span> Azure  预付费产品购买申请表页面</span>，你可以根据需要选择“个人申请”或“企业申请”。</h2>
					<table width="100%">
					<tr style="background-color:#4f81bd">
						<td style="color:#fff">若您选择的是 “个人申请”：</td>
						<td style="color:#fff">若您选择的是 “企业申请”：</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td width="50%">
							<dl>
								<dd>1) 输入手机号码后，进行手机验证即可进入下一步。</dd>
								<dd><a href="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step02_1_01.jpg" id="pia-application-step02_1_01" target="_blank"><img src="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step02_1_01.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a></dd>
							</dl>
						</td>
						<td>
							<dl>
								<dd>1) 输入手机号码后，进行手机验证即可进入下一步。</dd>
								<dd><a href="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step02_2_01.jpg" id="pia-application-step02_2_01" target="_blank"><img src="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step02_2_01.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a></dd>
							</dl>
						</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>
							<dl>
								
								<dd>2) 填写申请人姓名、身份证字号、邮箱，并上传您的身份证正反面照片后，点击“提交”。您将立即获得实名认证的审核结果，若审核通过，您将自动进入注册页面。</dd>
								<dd><a href="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step02_1_02.jpg" id="pia-application-step02_1_02" target="_blank"><img src="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step02_1_02.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a></dd>
							</dl>
						</td>
						<td >
							<dl>
								
								<dd>2) 填写申请人姓名、邮箱、企业全称、统一信用代码，并上传企业营业执照图片后，点击“提交”。您将立即获得企业实名认证的审核结果，若审核通过，您将自动进入注册页面。</dd>
								<dd><a href="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step02_2_02.jpg" id="pia-application-step02_2_02" target="_blank"><img src="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step02_2_02.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a></dd>
							</dl>
						</td>
					</tr>
				</table>
				<p>请点击<a href="/pricing/pia-waiting-list/?form-type=identityauth" target="_blank">Azure 预付费产品购买申请表</a></p>
				</div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>
				<div class="step-icon"><span>3</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs hidden-sm">3.</span> 通过实名认证之后，您将进入<span>注册页面</span>，请填写您的个人信息，并创建域名信息，点击检查域名可用性。</h2>
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs hidden-sm">3.</span> 确认域名可用后，请新建您的用户名和密码等信息，完成手机验证后，点击“继续”。</h2>
					<a href="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step_03.png" id="pia-application-step_03" target="_blank"><img src="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step_03.png" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
				</div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>
				<div class="step-icon"><span>4</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs hidden-sm">4.</span> 之后来到<span>登录页面</span>，输入您在上一步设定的用户名、密码即可登录账户，进行付款。</h2>
						<a href="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step_04.jpg" id="pia-application-step_04" target="_blank"><img src="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step_04.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
				</div>
				<div class="clearfix"></div>
				<div class="step-icon"><span>5</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs hidden-sm">5.</span> 进入<span>付款页面</span>之后，您可以选择“支付宝”、“电汇“或“银联在线支付”进行付款。</h2>
					<div class="col-md-6">
					<a href="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step_05_1.png" id="pia-application-step_05_1" target="_blank"><img src="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step_05_1.png" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-6"><a href="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step_05_2.png" id="pia-application-step_05_2" target="_blank"><img src="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step_05_2.png" title="点击查看原图"/></a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<p style="float:clear-both"> 线上支付（包括支付宝与银联在线最低支付金额为 1,000 元人民币，电汇最低支付金额为 5,000 元人民币，电汇流程详情请参考<a id="pricing-billing-pia-signup_wire-transfer-overview" href="//docs.azure.cn/zh-cn/billing/billing-pay-for-subscription-via-wire-transfer/" target="_blank">电汇说明</a>）</p>
					<p>温馨提示：后续的充值可根据每次需求变更支付方式。</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="clearfix"></div>
				<div class="step-icon"><span>6</span></div>
				<div class="step-container">
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs hidden-sm">6.</span> 支付成功后，系统将自动带你来到<span>账户管理页面</span>，可以看到账户的额度为 1,000 元人民币。</h2>
					<h2><span class="hidden-xs hidden-sm">6.</span> 至此，您就可以开始享受 Azure 服务，有效期为一年。</h2>
					<div>
					<a href="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step_06_1.jpg" id="pia-application-step_06_1" target="_blank"><img src="//wacndevelop.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/pia-application-step_06_1.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a></div>
					<p> 在使用期间，您可通过官网右上方的<a id="pricing-billing-pia-signup_windowsazure" href="https://portal.azure.cn/" target="_blank">登录 Azure 门户</a>进入账户页面，随时进行订阅充值续航。</p>
					<div><a href="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/azure-1rmb-trial-application-and-pia-step_06_2.jpg" id="pia-application-step_06_2" target="_blank"><img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/pricing/billing/azure-1rmb-trial-application-and-pia-step_06_2.jpg" title="点击查看原图"/></a></div>
				</div>
            </div>
    ]]>
    </bodyText>
